{
  "_doc": "Committed retrieval-quality benchmark. Persona graph (KO+EN) + labeled queries by category. Run: npm run bench (uses LOCAL_EMBEDDING_MODEL, default bge-m3 — auto-downloads). Ground truth = expect[] of memory ids; [] means the query must return nothing (not-found). Edit deliberately; this is a regression guard.",
